column1: # target       : target A used in single or double ratio
# singleR_A_c12_mf      : single ratio of target A_MF / C12_MF (per proton)
# singleR_A_c12_src      : single ratio of target A_SRC / C12_SRC (per proton)
# singleR_per_proton      : single ratio of target A(SRC/MF) (per proton)
# singleR_per_proton_err  : uncertainty in single ratio (per proton)
# doubleR      : double ratio of target A(SRC/MF) relative to C12 (SRC/MF)
# N: Z: A      : # of neutrons (N): protons(Z): nucleons (A): for target A
